    "• Navigate all the way back to **Locations** in the file picker." : {
      "comment" : "A step in the process of exporting a firmware file.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Gehe zum **Standorten** in der Dateiauswahl zurück."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Vuelva a navegar hasta las **Ubicaciones** en el seleccionador de archivos."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Vai indietro fino a **Posizioni** nel picker di file"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "回到文件选择器中，找到所有位置"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant-TW" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "回到文件選單中的**位置**"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• Select your USB device and tap **Save**." : {
      "comment" : "A step in the process of saving the firmware to a USB.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Wähle dein USB-Gerät und tippe auf **Speichern**."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Seleccione su dispositivo USB y haga clic en **Guardar**."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Seleziona il tuo dispositivo USB e premi **Salva**."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "请选择您的USB设备并点击**保存**"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant-TW" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "選擇您的USB裝置並按**儲存**"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• Tap the **Save Firmware to USB** button below." : {
      "comment" : "A step in the firmware update process.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Drücke die Schaltfläche \"Firmware speichern auf USB\" unten."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Presiona el botón **Guardar Firmware en USB** a continuación."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Tocca il pulsante \"Salva Firmware su USB\" sotto."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "点击下面的**将固件保存到USB**按钮"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant-TW" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "請按下下方的**將固件儲存到USB**按鈕"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• The filename will be a random string ending in `.uf2` to prevent iOS caching." : {
      "comment" : "A note that the filename of the downloaded firmware is random.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Der Dateiname wird eine zufällige Zeichenkette mit der Endung `.uf2` sein, um iOS-Caching zu verhindern."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "El nombre del archivo será una cadena aleatoria que termina en `.uf2` para evitar el caché de iOS."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Il nome del file di firmware scaricato sarà una stringa casuale terminante con `.uf2` per prevenire la memorizzazione in cache su iOS."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "下载的固件文件名将是一个随机字符串，以`.uf2`结尾，以防止iOS缓存。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant-TW" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "下載的軟體檔名將是隨機生成的以`.uf2`結尾的字串，以防止 iOS 緩存。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• You may see an error saying the file could not be saved. This is normal, as the device disconnects immediately after updating." : {
      "comment" : "A note that explains why you may see an error when saving the firmware.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Du siehst möglicherweise einen Fehler, der besagt, dass das Datei nicht gespeichert werden konnte. Das ist normal, da das Gerät sofort nach dem Update entkoppelt wird."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Puede que veas un error diciendo que el archivo no pudo ser guardado. Esto es normal, ya que el dispositivo se desconecta inmediatamente después de actualizarse."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Potresti vedere un errore che dice che il file non può essere salvato. Questo è normale, poiché il dispositivo si disconnette immediatamente dopo l'aggiornamento."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "您可能会看到一个错误提示文件无法保存，这是正常的，因为设备在更新后立即断开连接。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant-TW" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "您可能會看到一個錯誤訊息，表示檔案無法儲存。這是正常的，因為設備在更新後立即斷開連線。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
