    "The most recent public key for this node does not match the previously recorded key. Verify who you are messaging with by comparing public keys in person or over the phone." : {
      "comment" : "Text displayed in a help item that describes a public key mismatch error.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Das aktuellste öffentliche Schlüssel für diesen Knoten entspricht nicht dem zuvor aufgezeichneten Schlüssel. Überprüfen Sie, wer Sie mit dem öffentlichen Schlüssel kommunizieren, indem Sie ihn persönlich oder telefonisch vergleichen."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "El clave pública más reciente para este nodo no coincide con la clave previamente registrada. Verifique quién está enviando el mensaje comparando las claves públicas en persona o por teléfono."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Il più recente chiave pubblica per questo nodo non corrisponde alla chiave precedentemente registrata. Verifica chi stai contattando confrontando le chiavi pubbliche di persona o per telefono."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "该节点的最近公钥与之前记录的公钥不匹配。请通过亲自或电话对比公钥来验证您与谁通信。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant-TW" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "此節點的最新公鑰與之前記錄的公鑰不匹配。請透過親自或電話比較公鑰來確認與誰通話。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The node has been heard recently and is considered online." : {
      "comment" : "Text",
