    },
    "The primary channel handles broadcast traffic. Add secondary channels for separate messaging groups, each secured by their own key. [Learn more](https://meshtastic.org/docs/configuration/tips/)" : {
      "comment" : "A description of the channels feature.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Der Hauptkanal verarbeitet Broadcast-Verkehr. Füge sekundäre Kanäle für verschiedene Nachrichtengruppen hinzu, die jeweils mit ihrem eigenen Schlüssel gesichert sind. [Mehr erfahren](https://meshtastic.org/docs/configuration/tips/)"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "El canal principal maneja el tráfico de transmisión. Agregue canales secundarios para grupos de mensajería separados, cada uno cifrado con su propia clave. [Aprenda más](https://meshtastic.org/docs/configuration/tips/)"
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Il canale principale gestisce il traffico di trasmissione. Aggiungi canali secondari per gruppi di messaggistica separati, ciascuno protetto da una propria chiave. [Scopri di più](https://meshtastic.org/docs/configuration/tips/)"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "主频道负责广播流量，添加次要频道用于独立的消息组，每个组都使用其自身的密钥进行加密。[了解更多](https://meshtastic.org/docs/configuration/tips/)"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant-TW" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "主頻道負責廣播流量。為每個獨立訊息群組添加副頻道，每個群組都使用其獨特的密碼進行保護。[了解更多](https://meshtastic.org/docs/configuration/tips/)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The primary channel must use the default key to perform a discovery scan." : {
